{"tid":335990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(口德考驗)中國學生亂玩鞭炮 肚破腸流跑1公里求救","createTime":"2017-07-26T05:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T09:04:55.000Z","uid":41351,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1afea9427d4ae9e791e5118ec29ffff4a4cf780c","tid":335990,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國一名14歲的國中生，因為將鞭炮裡的火藥倒出來玩，意外引發爆炸，他身旁的鐵罐被炸碎，碎片就這樣射進他的肚子裡，開出兩個大洞，腸子也因此跑了出來。少年跑了1公里多求救，至今仍未脫離險境，但他的父親打工薪水微薄，母親有精神疾患，這家人無法負擔醫藥費。<br />\n綜合媒體報導，意外發生在13日，中國黑龍江哈爾濱市賓縣的14歲少年王雨成到鄰居家玩，好奇將火藥倒出來玩，意外爆炸後炸碎一旁的鐵罐，碎片射進身體，造成他肚破腸流，有如被恐怖份子的鐵管炸彈炸傷般。據王雨成的李姓嬸嬸表示，王雨成的母親當時也在現場，腳也被炸傷，但由於患有精神病無法照顧孩子，因此王雨成才會帶著傷跑了1公里多求救，所幸有村民目睹幫他叫救護車。<br />\n<br />\n醫生表示，王雨成左下肢外傷、開放性腹外傷、急性腹膜炎、感染中毒性休克、小腸破裂、橫結腸破裂。由於腸子已被截斷，只能靠肚子上的管子排出糞便。而王雨成住院治療9天，共花掉15萬元人民幣（約67.39萬元台幣），還必須再進行兩次手術，然而，王家無力負擔手術費。<br />\n<br />\n王雨成的李姓嬸嬸無奈表示：「孩子到現在高燒不退，精神恍惚，一會清醒一會昏迷，醫生說現在的情況還可能引起併發症，有肝腎衰竭的可能」，院方已經給了病危通知書，情況並不樂觀，但由於無力負擔醫療費用，只能從加護病房轉到普通術後觀察病房。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.101mediaimage.com/img/file/1510328229ce466.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.101mediaimage.com%2Fimg%2Ffile%2F1510328229ce466.jpg&h=3ef949a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpjnKayP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpjnKayP.jpg&h=88b1fe8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2143254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2143254&d=mcaRc0iEmC6WJm6dfPyqKi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=cd42dc99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2143254&h=221d8b69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2143254</a><br />\n大家有D咩鼓勵說話"},{"pid":"740639ce51a79fd29dbde009a51ad2aaedbf463f","tid":335990,"uid":995,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"咪咁快死呀 呢世慢慢做支那狗"},{"pid":"9c604eb45d43fce1390c890198fc4f76a3497b65","tid":335990,"uid":14103,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"唯有安慰佢家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你個仔咁撚柒 又咁撚蠢 死左佢 生過另一個啦"},{"pid":"3d2707189905d7f72b3c607d23ac9f0b3f8c19a3","tid":335990,"uid":52068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"一定要堅持落去啊！！！人生流流長，加油！"},{"pid":"7fe1dd76fd7a7ae81f920fa5e22e8730f07eed14","tid":335990,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"快快投胎做美國人啦"},{"pid":"0a179b1c005eb2554e6c273cce06e525713aba2f","tid":335990,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T05:59:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a678c7958ca74ccf2c0a2086d48fd007ded0e082","tid":335990,"uid":71257,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:13:34.000Z","msg":"咁幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爆左肚仲跑去醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfb5a009ffb49303fb3ad0bfd7b8aaf6bd084d3","tid":335990,"uid":20241,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/141521_9d44d47bc1a91aec40aa04e22ccb1cda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F141521_9d44d47bc1a91aec40aa04e22ccb1cda.jpg&h=ad63cca0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1047160734d36ec383d6bf23f4f2f36bfd3ef42","tid":335990,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T06:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爆左肚仲跑去醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肚破腸流都頂得住<i